///////////////////////////////////////  List of new features added to the app ////////////////////////////////////

** Line Chart Support – Replaced scatter plot with a working line chart for numeric/date data.

** Chart Type Selector – Users can choose between bar, pie, or line charts.

** Data Filtering Panel – Added interactive filters for categorical and numeric columns.

** Improved Word Cloud – Selectable text column with better error handling.

** UI Enhancements – Clear layout, emojis, titles, and better visual styling.

** Column Normalization – Auto-strips and lowercases column names.

** Better Chart Logic – Clean limits, labels, and color use for clarity and storytelling.

/////////////////////////////////////////////////////   END  ////////////////////////////////////////////////////
